  "mermaid": "graph TD\n    A[DNA Replication Error] --> B{Error Type?}\n    \n    B -->|Base-Base Mismatch| C[G-T, A-C, etc.]\n    B -->|Insertion-Deletion Loop| D[IDL 1-4 nt]\n    B -->|Complex Error| E[Multiple Errors]\n    \n    C --> F[Helix Distortion]\n    D --> F\n    E --> F\n    \n    %% MutS Recognition\n    F --> G[MutS Homodimer Scanning]\n    G --> H{Mismatch Detection?}\n    \n    H -->|No Mismatch| I[Continue Scanning]\n    I --> G\n    H -->|Mismatch Found| J[MutS Binding]\n    \n    J --> K{Mismatch Type Verification?}\n    K -->|G-T Most Recognized| L[Strong MutS Binding]\n    K -->|Other Mismatches| M[Variable Binding Affinity]\n    K -->|IDL| N[IDL-Specific Recognition]\n    \n    L --> O[ATP Binding to MutS]\n    M --> O\n    N --> O\n    \n    O --> P[MutS Conformational Change]\n    P --> Q[Sliding Clamp Formation]\n    \n    %% MutL Recruitment\n    Q --> R[MutL Homodimer Recruitment]\n    R --> S{MutS-MutL Complex?}\n    S -->|Formation| T[MutS-MutL-DNA Ternary Complex]\n    S -->|Failed| U[Abortive Recognition]\n    \n    T --> V[ATP Hydrolysis]\n    V --> W[MutS-MutL Translocation]\n    W --> X{GATC Site Search?}\n    \n    %% Strand Discrimination\n    X -->|Scanning| Y[Searching for GATC]\n    Y --> Z{Hemimethylated GATC?}\n    \n    Z -->|Not Found| AA[Continue Search]\n    AA --> Y\n    Z -->|Found| AB{Methylation Status?}\n    \n    AB -->|Hemimethylated| AC[Dam Methylation Site]\n    AB -->|Fully Methylated| AD[Wrong Strand]\n    AB -->|Unmethylated| AE[Abnormal State]\n    \n    %% MutH Activation\n    AC --> AF{Strand Identity?}\n    AF -->|New Strand Unmethylated| AG[Correct Target Identified]\n    AF -->|Old Strand Methylated| AH[Preserve This Strand]\n    \n    AG --> AI[MutH Endonuclease Recruitment]\n    AI --> AJ{MutL Activates MutH?}\n    AJ -->|Yes| AK[MutH Activation]\n    AJ -->|No| AL[Failed Activation]\n    \n    AK --> AM[MutH Incision at GATC]\n    AM --> AN[Nick in Unmethylated Strand]\n    AN --> AO{Nick Position?}\n    \n    AO -->|5' to Mismatch| AP[5' Nick]\n    AO -->|3' to Mismatch| AQ[3' Nick]\n    \n    %% Excision - 5' to 3' Direction\n    AP --> AR{Exonuclease Selection?}\n    AR -->|RecJ| AS[5' to 3' ssDNA Exonuclease]\n    AR -->|ExoVII| AT[Alternative 5' to 3']\n    \n    AS --> AU[/Degrade Toward Mismatch/]\n    AT --> AU\n    AU --> AV[Pass Mismatch Site]\n    AV --> AW[/Continue Degradation/]\n    AW --> AX[SSB Coating ssDNA]\n    \n    %% Excision - 3' to 5' Direction\n    AQ --> AY{Exonuclease Selection?}\n    AY -->|ExoI| AZ[3' to 5' ssDNA Exonuclease]\n    AY -->|ExoX| BA[Alternative 3' to 5']\n    AY -->|ExoVII| BB[Bidirectional Option]\n    \n    AZ --> BC[/Degrade Toward Mismatch/]\n    BA --> BC\n    BB --> BC\n    BC --> BD[Pass Mismatch Site]\n    BD --> BE[/Continue Degradation/]\n    BE --> BF[SSB Protection]\n    \n    %% Termination of Excision\n    AW --> BG{Excision Complete?}\n    BE --> BG\n    BG -->|Sufficient| BH[/Stop Signal/]\n    BG -->|Insufficient| BI(\\1)\n    \n    BH --> BJ[Single-Strand Gap]\n    BJ --> BK{Gap Size?}\n    BK -->|Short <100 nt| BL[Small Gap]\n    BK -->|Long >1000 nt| BM[Large Gap]\n    \n    %% DNA Resynthesis\n    BL --> BN[DNA Pol III Recognition]\n    BM --> BN\n    BN --> BO{Holoenzyme Assembly?}\n    BO -->|Complete| BP[Processive Synthesis]\n    BO -->|Partial| BQ[Distributive Synthesis]\n    \n    BP --> BR[dNTP Incorporation]\n    BR --> BS[Rapid Gap Filling]\n    BS --> BT[High Fidelity Synthesis]\n    BT --> BU[Gap Filled]\n    \n    %% Ligation\n    BU --> BV{Nick Sealing?}\n    BV -->|Ready| BW[DNA Ligase]\n    BV -->|Not Ready| BX[Additional Processing]\n    \n    BW --> BY[NAD+ Ligase LigA]\n    BY --> BZ[Phosphodiester Bond]\n    BZ --> CA[Nick Sealed]\n    \n    CA --> CB[Restored DNA Helix]\n    CB --> CC{Repair Verification?}\n    CC -->|Successful| CD[High Fidelity DNA]\n    CC -->|Residual Error| CE[Secondary MMR]\n    \n    %% Final Outcomes\n    CD --> CF[1000x Error Reduction]\n    CF --> CG[Genome Stability]\n    CG --> CH[Cell Survival]\n    CH --> CI[Replication Fidelity]\n    \n    %% Error Pathways\n    U --> CJ[Mismatch Escapes]\n    AL --> CJ\n    AD --> CK[Wrong Strand Risk]\n    AE --> CL[Dam Methylation Defect]\n    CE --> CM[Persistent Mismatch]\n    \n    CJ --> CN[Reduced Fidelity]\n    CK --> CN\n    CM --> CN\n    CN --> CO(\\1)\n    \n    %% Regulation\n    AX --> CP{SSB Saturation?}\n    BF --> CP\n    CP -->|Sufficient| BG\n    CP -->|Limited| CQ[/Slower Degradation/]\n    \n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n\n    %% Semantic Color Styling\n    style B fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style A fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style C fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style D fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style E fill:#51cf66,color:#fff\n    style F fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style G fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style H fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style I fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style J fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style K fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style L fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style M fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style N fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style O fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style P fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Q fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style R fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style S fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style T fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style U fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style V fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style W fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style X fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style Y fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style Z fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AA fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AB fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AC fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AD fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AE fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AF fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AG fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AH fill:#b3e5fc,color:#000\n    style AI fill:#42a5f5,color:#fff\n    style AJ fill:#7950f2,color:#fff\n    style AK fi